into motion. Right?

207
00:20:49,536 --> 00:20:53,564
I'm going to team up with Johan
and make the world mine.

208
00:20:54,107 --> 00:20:55,438
Right?

209
00:20:56,443 --> 00:20:58,878
What are you going to
do about my ear?!

210
00:20:59,379 --> 00:21:02,280
You can't interfere
with my plan.

211
00:21:02,716 --> 00:21:04,241
You can't!

212
00:21:04,317 --> 00:21:05,284
Drop your gun!

213
00:21:10,590 --> 00:21:11,523
Kenzo?

214
00:21:23,670 --> 00:21:31,670
Johan told me to tell his sister,
where he was if she came

215
00:21:32,312 --> 00:21:37,716
and that his sister would
probably kill me afterwards.

216
00:21:38,785 --> 00:21:41,584
Why won't you kill me?

217
00:21:47,227 --> 00:21:48,285
Your memories...

218
00:21:48,762 --> 00:21:50,821
Did you get them all back?

219
00:21:52,766 --> 00:21:53,392
Yes.

220
00:21:53,967 --> 00:21:57,665
Then why won't you kill me?

221
00:22:03,510 --> 00:22:09,745
You must be overflowing
with hatred, anger and grief.

222
00:22:14,888 --> 00:22:18,688
What are we?
You know, don't you?

223
00:22:20,727 --> 00:22:22,217
I've heard things...

224
00:22:26,633 --> 00:22:30,627
about how you twins were born.

